Started to trend low during show performance and ate two Welch’s fruit snacks packs totaling 38g of carbs. Looked at dexcom again in 15mins and saw that those carbs had made no change on blood sugar levels. I ate two more fruit snack packs (38g carbs) and thought it might have been too much but only reach as high as 180s blood glucose before trending downward again.
